+- Spec: `e2e/staff-documentation-workspace.e2e.spec.ts`
+- Screenshot: `documentation-checklist-blockers.png`
+- Screenshot: `documentation-security-workflow.png`
+- Screenshot: `documentation-restricted-state.png`
